# vim-metarw-webdav

webdav filesystem for vim

## Requirements

- [metarw](https://github.com/kana/vim-metarw)
- [davc](https://github.com/mattn/davc)

## Usage

### List file system on webdav

```
:edit webdav://server/
```

```
:edit webdav:/server/path/to/file.txt
```

If you use https, try to open `webdavs://`.

### Add current buffer on file system

`:write webdavs:/server/bar`

### Update current

`:write`


